workflow.name: Capture and nurture AI agency leads with Google Gemini, Outlook and Sheets
workflow.description:
# AI Agent Lead Funnel for AI Agencies  
## An End-to-End Automation That Turns Demos Into Booked Calls

This n8n workflow is a **full inbound ‚Üí outbound hybrid funnel** designed for AI agencies.  
It captures warm leads through instant AI value, then automatically follows up with **personalized, context-aware outreach and reminders** until the lead either replies or books a call.

No cold scraping. No manual follow-ups. Just leverage + timing.

---

## üöÄ How the Workflow Works

---

## üìã PART 1 ‚Äî Lead Capture & Instant Value

### **1 ‚Äî Share High-Impact AI Image Edits**
You post before/after examples using the **NanoBanna / Gemini image-editing model** on social platforms.  
Each post includes a link to a lightweight form.

The visual results do the selling for you.

---

### **2 ‚Äî Lead Submits Image & Details**
The form collects:
- Image upload  
- Edit instructions  
- Name  
- Email  
- Company name  

This filters for **high-intent prospects only**.

---

### **3 ‚Äî AI Edits the Image Instantly**
Once submitted, the workflow:
- Sends the image + instructions to the AI image editor  
- Preserves lighting and camera angle unless specified  
- Generates a polished result in seconds  

---

### **4 ‚Äî Result Delivered via Email**
The edited image is emailed directly to the user with:
- A friendly confirmation message  
- Soft positioning for future work  

This establishes trust before any sales motion happens.

---

### **5 ‚Äî Lead Is Logged Automatically**
All lead data is saved to Google Sheets:
- Name  
- Company  
- Email  
- Timestamp  

This becomes your **live CRM of warm inbound leads**.

---

## ü§ñ PART 2 ‚Äî AI-Driven Personalized Outreach

### **6 ‚Äî AI Analyzes the Lead**
An AI sales agent:
- Looks at the company name + context  
- Reviews a library of proven automation ideas  
- Either selects the best fit **or creates a simple custom one**

---

### **7 ‚Äî AI Writes a Personalized Outreach Email**
The agent generates a short email that:
- Mentions a **specific automation already built**
- States you can help implement it quickly
- Invites them to book a call via your calendar

No marketing fluff. No generic pitches.  
Every email feels hand-written.

---

### **8 ‚Äî Outreach Email Is Sent Automatically**
The email is sent from your inbox (Outlook, Gmail, SMTP, etc.) and includes:
- Their name  
- Their company  
- A clear calendar booking link  

---

## üì¨ PART 3 ‚Äî Smart Follow-Up System

### **9 ‚Äî Wait 48 Hours**
The workflow pauses to give the lead time to respond naturally.

---

### **10 ‚Äî Check for a Reply**
After 48 hours:
- If the lead replied ‚Üí they are tagged as **Interested**
- If no reply ‚Üí continue to follow-up

(Current reply detection is placeholder logic and can be swapped for a live inbox listener.)

---

### **11 ‚Äî AI Writes a Polite Follow-Up**
If there‚Äôs no response, an AI agent writes:
- A short, non-pushy follow-up  
- Referencing the original automation idea  
- Under 60 words  

---

### **12 ‚Äî Follow-Up Email Is Sent**
The follow-up goes out automatically and keeps the conversation alive without manual effort.

---

## üìà Why This Workflow Converts So Well

### **Instant Value First**
Leads experience AI results before being pitched anything.

### **Context-Aware Outreach**
Every email is personalized based on the lead, not a template.

### **Built-In Persistence**
The system follows up automatically ‚Äî no leads fall through the cracks.

### **Fully Automated**
Once live, this workflow handles:
- Lead capture  
- AI delivery  
- Outreach  
- Follow-ups  
- CRM updates  

You just keep posting content.

---

## üîß Setup Requirements

To deploy this workflow, connect:

- **Google Gemini API** (image editing + agents)  
- **Email provider**
  - Outlook  
  - Gmail  
  - SMTP  
- **Google Sheets**
  - Columns: Name, Company, Email, Time, Status  
- **Calendar booking link**
  - Example: `https://cal.com/your-link`

All credentials are modular and easily swappable.

---

## üéØ Summary

This n8n automation turns attention into action by:
1. Delivering immediate AI value  
2. Following up with relevant, personalized ideas  
3. Nudging leads toward a booked call ‚Äî automatically  

It‚Äôs not just a lead funnel.  
It‚Äôs an **AI sales assistant that runs 24/7**.

nodes.name: AI Sales Agent - Idea Picker & Email Writer

options.systemMessage:
You are an AI sales engineer.

Your task:
1. Analyze the company name and context.
2. Either select ONE automation idea from the list provided OR create a very simple custom one.
3. Write a short, confident email saying:
   - This automation is already built
   - We can help implement it for them
   - Include a call-to-action to book a call

Constraints:
- Keep it under 150 words
- Sound casual but professional
- Do NOT sound like marketing copy
- Be specific about the automation chosen

Return JSON in this format:
{
  "chosenIdea": "the automation idea you selected or created",
  "emailBody": "the complete email text"
}

‚Äì Hyrum

parameters.content:
## üìã PART 1: Lead Capture

Captures leads through form submission, processes images with AI, and stores contact info in Google Sheets.

## ü§ñ PART 2: AI Outreach

AI analyzes company context, selects relevant automation idea, and generates personalized outreach email automatically.

## üì¨ PART 3: Follow-up System

Waits 48 hours, checks for replies, sends AI-generated follow-up if no response, or tags lead as interested if they replied.

## üîÑ How It Works

**Step 1:** Lead fills form ‚Üí Image edited + contact saved
**Step 2:** AI picks automation idea ‚Üí Writes personalized email
**Step 3:** Email sent with calendar link
**Step 4:** Wait 48 hours
**Step 5:** Check for reply:
  ‚Ä¢ No reply ‚Üí AI writes follow-up ‚Üí Send
  ‚Ä¢ Reply received ‚Üí Tag as "Interested" in sheet

**Result:** Automated lead qualification + nurturing at scale

## üìñ Setup Instructions

1. Add Google Gemini API credentials
2. Connect Microsoft Outlook account
3. Connect Google Sheets (create a sheet with columns: Name, Company, Email, Time, Status)
4. Update calendar booking link in outreach email (currently: https://cal.com/quartersmart/intro)
5. Customize automation ideas list in the "üìö Automation Ideas Library" node
6. Update email signatures with your name and company
7. Test with a sample form submission

data.details:
The IF node can be used to implement binary conditional logic in your workflow. You can set up one-to-many conditions to evaluate each item of data being inputted into the node. That data will either evaluate to TRUE or FALSE and route out of the node accordingly.

This node has multiple types of conditions: Bool, String, Number, and Date & Time.
